   DEBUG: 2026-03-24 06:54:43,111:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  appears in the signal model name to decide which loop to use.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-24 06:54:43,112:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 1: Write the Model Class
