   DEBUG: 2026-03-24 06:54:43,126:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  method. The forward signature depends on which training loop you target.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-24 06:54:43,127:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: For the GNN-style loop (
   DEBUG: 2026-03-24 06:54:43,128:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: data_train_gnn
